description.narrative: 1.3 Increased capacity to provide health services that are sensitive and responsive to the needs of adolescents and improved knowledge on healthy behaviours, which contributes to Adolescent Health And Nutrition, Adolescent Health And Nutrition (Covid). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, children, including newborns and adolescents, and women of reproductive age have improved and equitable access to and use of high-impact quality health interventions and improved healthy behaviors.
